'''fullscreen_bpp''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Sets the bpp to use in fullscreen mode.

<pre>
[win32]
fullscreen_bpp = 8
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 8 | 16 | 32 ]

'''Default:''' 8


